                    destination MAC address value. xx-xx-xx-xx-xx-xx."
               ::= {     sm48tat4xarpACLACEEntry 22 }

    sm48tat4xarpACLACEEtherType OBJECT-TYPE
               SYNTAX      Integer32(-1..65535)
