               MAX-ACCESS  read-create
               STATUS      current
               DESCRIPTION
                   "Specify whether frames can hit the action according to
                    their target hardware address field (THA) settings.
                    default: 2,
                    0: RARP frames where THA is not equal to the DMAC address.
                    1: RARP frames where THA is equal to the DMAC address.
                    2: Any - Don't care.
                    3: No data."
               DEFVAL  { any }
               ::= {     sm48tat4xarpACLACEEntry 27 }

