                   "Specify whether frames can hit the action according to
                    their ARP/RARP hardware address space (HRD) settings.
                    default: 2,
                    0: ARP/RARP frames where the HLD is not equal to Ethernet(1).
                    1: ARP/RARP frames where the HLD is equal to Ethernet(1).
                    2: Any - Don't care.
                    3: No data."
               DEFVAL  { any }
               ::= {     sm48tat4xarpACLACEEntry 29 }

    sm48tat4xarpACLACEArpFlagsEthernet OBJECT-TYPE
               SYNTAX      INTEGER { notEqualIp(0), equalIp(1),
                                     any(2), noData(3)}
               MAX-ACCESS  read-create
               STATUS      current
               DESCRIPTION
                   "Specify whether frames can hit the action
